    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is ready for someone with a bit of mechanical know-how to bring it back to its former glory! While it's in poor condition and will need some dedicated TLC and repairs, it represents a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for a hobbyist or anyone looking for a solid parts car.",
