    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable project car or basic commuter for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are functional, though you can expect some minor leaks and a less-than-perfect idle. Cosmetically, the exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading paint, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It has been recently serviced for basic fluids, but it will likely need new tires and brake pads in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that reflects its age and mileage, offered at a price that leaves room for the necessary repairs.",
      "price": 19500.0,
