    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has been meticulously maintained, featuring a robust powertrain and a well-appointed interior that remains in commendable condition. It offers a balanced synthesis of performance and reliability, representing an exceptional value for the discerning driver who demands quality and consistent performance. We invite you to experience the caliber of this well-preserved automobile.",
      "price": 34800.0,
