    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014definitely ready for your next road trip! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54B32 engine. This unit features a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS rebuild, addressing the primary weak points of the chassis. The S54's individual throttle bodies provide exceptional throttle response, feeding power through a six-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in and reduced body roll. While the exterior shows minor road wear, the drivetrain is in excellent health with recent valve lash adjustments and consistent oil analysis. This is a driver-focused example with a rigid chassis and a linear power band, ready for spirited canyon carving or track day duty.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    }
